    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. She\u2019s in absolute showroom condition and looks just like she did the day she rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, keeping it sparkling clean and running like a total dream. It\u2019s a super smooth ride and honestly feels brand new inside and out. I\u2019m sad to see her go, but I know she\u2019s going to make her next owner so happy! Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
