    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a pristine, collector-grade specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized volumetric efficiency across the entire power band. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and tactile engagement. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural and internal integrity remains at factory standards. The chassis retains its original suspension geometry and damping rates, offering the uncompromised handling dynamics that define the M-division legacy. Truly a turn-key acquisition for the purist seeking mechanical excellence.",
